title: NBA-Explorer-Aplication
content: This is an application created to have the ability to create, read, update and delete on a topic that I was passionate about in this case the National Basketball Association in other words the NBA. I had also added the ability to add media types to Teams and Players. The application is created with C#, this application allow user to upload media such gif, png, and jpeg to the program.

title: Offline Dog game
content: This game was a spinoff of the famous and icon offline dinosaur game that we all love when the internet goes down. This game is mainly created with CSS.
